A good beginning but needs some improvements. When "Remove two sides" is selected and "Only play selected part" is checked and you press the play button then only the selected part is played as expected. However if you tap anywhere in the selected part to start playback then the file plays right to the end of the original file and not just to the end of the selected part. So if you are trying to pinpoint an end to a selected section you have to play the whole selected part each time. What really needs to be fixed though is when a file is saved the file name is the same as the original but all the spaces are removed from the original name resulting in one long name. Also what you are saving the file as is added to the end of the name (music, ringtone, notification) with no option to disable this. Because of these two things each and evey file name must be edited. If a person is only doing the odd edit with this app these two things are only a minor inconvenience but if you plan on using the app a lot these two things will become very annoying.
